de.sciss.jcollider
Class Synth

java.lang.Object
  de.sciss.jcollider.Node
      de.sciss.jcollider.Synth
All Implemented Interfaces:
Constants, TreeNode
public class Synth
extends Node

Mimics SCLang's Synth class, that is, it's a client side representation of a synth in the synthesis graph

Version:
0.23, 02-Oct-05
Author:
Hanns Holger Rutz
Warning:
this is a quick direct translation from SClang which is largely untested. before all methods have been thoroughly verified, excepted some of them to be wrong or behave different than expected. what certainly works is instantiation and new-messages
